name: Endurance #4
description:
Building endurance doesn't only involve long, low power efforts. In this session, we challenge your aerobic energy pathways with a range of efforts. Opening with a 10min Zone 2 effort, we build into a some neuromuscular work, before finishing with a Zone 3 effort that starts at the top of the range and gradually decreases.
